{"tid":501652,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【亞視永恆】手機Apps月費盛惠38蚊 無綫班底搞ATV得唔得？","createTime":"2017-12-17T05:30:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-18T04:44:01.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"ba5ebd2020c7b223a41e1a62500a3d7a2e07ead2","tid":501652,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T05:30:30.000Z","msg":"舊年熄機嘅亞視，將會以手機Apps同OTT平台復活，為咗重生，新亞視搵咗一班無綫班底幕後運作，包括前製作總監吳雨擔任亞視行政總裁、前企業傳訊部副總監曾醒明做亞視對外事務部總監，又有前助理總經理區偉林擔任亞視營運總裁、前製作部總監何麗全做亞視高級顧問，以及前無綫資深監製林嘉穎做亞視製作部總監等等。<br />\n<br />\n之前《蘋果》已經率先爆無綫前總經理陳志雲會倒戈為亞視主持全新《百萬富翁》（新聞連結： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2iTVWRR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2iTVWRR&d=AUk8h6ar0TC32KR9bgoZ5jQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=8ecdf1fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2iTVWRR</a> ），而亞視除咗《百萬富翁》之外，另一個重頭戲係以超過2000萬買入范冰冰主演嘅重頭劇《贏天下》香港獨家播映權，同大陸同步播映。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》收到可靠消息，亞視鐵定喺下個月29日復播，而嚟緊星期一(18日)亞視喺麗思卡爾頓酒店舉行「亞洲電視數碼媒體有限公司重組啟航暨應用程式啟用儀式」當日開始，亞視個apps會先重播舊節目，到29號先會推出一系列新節目。至於亞視個新模式近似無綫myTV SUPER，有免費同收費，其中手機收費方面，每月月費係38蚊。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，新亞視除咗請嚟陳志雲、朱慧敏同曾華倩過檔做節目之外，重搵咗向海嵐、樂瞳、李麗蕊、蘇珊、陳彥行加盟，而亞視舊將方面，就搵咗劉鍚賢、朱慧珊、張家瑩、馮家俊、車車(張紫櫻)、劉家聰等回歸。<br />\n<br />\n而曾醒明被問到做亞視對外事務部總監時，佢話：「等18號電視台公佈啦。」<br />\n<br />\n更多娛聞，喺晒《娛果》<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.com/appledailyent\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Fappledailyent&d=AUk8h6ar0TC32KR9bgoZ5jQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=5b04c020\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/appledailyent</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20171217/57590845\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171217%2F57590845&d=AUk8h6ar0TC32KR9bgoZ5jQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=4349db09\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171217%2F57590845&h=aed269e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20171217/57590845</a>"},{"pid":"8dd669d4805be29748a1dad8ccf4cc065845e07a","tid":501652,"uid":21819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T05:42:20.000Z","msg":"改名先啦"},{"pid":"5a924022c4c337cdf85294f9e990f176e84b0c0a","tid":501652,"uid":5159,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T05:44:10.000Z","msg":"香港人有錢買iPhone 冇錢買WhatsApp, 你同佢地收月費都係想比狗屌姐"},{"pid":"e1fa812e88a61b82bad2cbea32936bd6f5e42350","tid":501652,"uid":90863,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T05:47:52.000Z","msg":"我同人share nextflix family plan都係廿幾蚊<br />\n更加唔好提節目同畫面質素<br />\n比錢睇亞視真係唔驚講出去比人笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebf2ce53b67ee5ebdce56e24d6b8983369939244","tid":501652,"uid":149879,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T05:49:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/17/134909_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F17%2F134909_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=813b45ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"88df418dcfcfce3d018369c96b5c6d52ab0be998","tid":501652,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T05:54:07.000Z","msg":"如果有新聞，都會支持"},{"pid":"3358b268fe369cbf45bab9fe149f9da350f41fc1","tid":501652,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T05:55:56.000Z","msg":"tvb 2號"},{"pid":"a91f673066797cfc1e93e05eef9d4086e2502c51","tid":501652,"uid":4661,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T05:57:35.000Z","msg":"亞視用無綫班底<br />\n無綫